<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3757] MetaType AD.validate() ignored mandatory fields without min, max or optionValues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3757</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If an attribute is required, but does not define its min, max or optionValues parameters, the validate() regards absent data as valid.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
